OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers will
OL,6,Fclear away this evening. Then dry with
OL,7,Fclear spells in the west, while
OL,8,Feastern areas will see rather murky
OL,9,Fconditions with a risk of mist, fog
OL,10,Fand drizzle.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FDry and settled. Cloudy at
OL,13,Ffirst with damp and murky conditions
OL,14,Ffor eastern coasts, but soon
OL,15,Fbrightening up with some good spells
OL,16,Fof sunshine. East coast chilly.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
