OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FDry
OL,6,Fand settled conditions with plenty of
OL,7,Fsunshine for most. Some patchy cloud
OL,8,Fmay linger around eastern coasts at
OL,9,Ftimes in the mornings. Chance of
OL,10,Fshowery rain Friday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
